settings.heading_1: At Docking Drawer, we’re committed to creating innovative electrical products with the highest levels of safety in mind. We started out that way, and we’re committed to continuing on that path.
settings.content_left: We are the market leader of in-drawer electrical outlets. Offering a full array of ETL Listed solutions, Docking Drawer is committed to charging and powering today’s connected lifestyle with innovative solutions. Our patented and simple-to-specify outlets offer a reliable way to add movable drawer outlets safely, while keeping your spaces organized. ​
settings.content_right: With a variety of charging and powering in-drawer outlet solutions designed to fit into all types of cabinets, Docking Drawer outlets can be installed in kitchen and bathroom cabinets - or in hospitality, campus and medical facilities - providing an innovative and functional power source with a clutter-free aesthetic.

settings.banner_paragraph_1: Charging series outlets are specifically designed to charge today's technology and feature a built-in circuit breaker preventing high power devices such as hair dryers from being used. ​
settings.banner_paragraph_2: Charging outlets are made for laptops, cell phones, tablets, fitness trackers, CPAP machines, and more.
settings.banner_paragraph_4: Need More Power? Our Style Drawer in-drawer powering outlets deliver 20 amps via a GFCI outlets to power devices such as hairdryers, blenders, tools, etc.

settings.outlet_content:
Charging Outlet

  • 4 versions - Blade, Blade USB, Blade Duo, and Blade Duo USB
  • 5 sizes available
​Features:
  • 2" - The least amount of space needed behind the drawer box
  • Eliminate the need to shorten drawer boxes
  • Ideal for wider drawers
  • Able to charge up to 8 devices at a time
​When to specify:
  • Can be specified during any phase of the project, whether it be at the beginning, middle or end.
Warranty:
  • 2 Year Warranty

Charging Outlet

  • 2 versions - Slim and Slim USB
  • 3 Sizes available
Features:
  • Requires 3" of space behind the drawer box
  • May require the drawer to be stepped down a drawer box size or shorted to make room for the outlet
  • Ideal for narrower drawer specifications
  • Able to charge up to 4 devices at a time
When to specify:
  • Typically specified in the beginning or middle phase of a project
Warranty:
  • 1 Year Warranty

Charging Outlet

  • 1 version - USB Narrow
  • 1 size available
Features:
  • Requires​ 5" of space behind the drawer box
  • May require the drawer to be stepped down a drawer box size or shorted to make room for the outlet
  • Narrowest charging outlet specifications
  • Able to charge up to 4 devices at a time
When to specify:
  • Typically specified in the beginning or middle phase of a project
Warranty
  • 1 Year Warranty

settings.banner_paragraph_1: Powering outlets are ideal for hair dryers, curling irons, and anything requiring up to 20 amps of current. Outlets feature a UL Listed thermostat that cuts power to the outlet in the event that the surrounding temperature exceeds 120˚F.
settings.banner_paragraph_2: Only need to charge your technology? Our charging outlets are designed for kitchen cabinets spaces, deliver 3 amps of current and are perfect for just charging cell phones, tablets, and laptops..

settings.outlet_content:
• 4 Models to choose from - Blade, Flush, Surface Mount, Duo
  • Sized by cabinet depth to ensure the outlet offers enough extension for the drawer to open completely
  • Finishes - Black, White, Stainless Steel
  • Outlet Specifications - 20 Amp, 125 Volt Receptacle/Outlet 20 Amp Feed-Through, Tamper-Resistant, Self-test SmartlockPro Slim GFCI
  • Electrical Connection - Hardwired
  • Mounts left or right and horizontally or vertically.
  • Works with side-mount, under-mount and soft closing glides.
  • ​Most specified powering in-drawer outlet is Style Drawer 21 Flush series outlets

If for some reason an outlet needs to be exchanged to another outlet series or size, Docking Drawer will happily accept exchanges. To initiate an exchange, please complete the Contact Us form. Once reviewed, a EGA form will be emailed with instructions on how to successfully return your order.
settings.return_content:
Docking Drawer wants you to be happy with your order. If for some reason however an outlet needs to be returned, Docking Drawer will happily accept returns. To initiate a return, please complete the Contact Us form. Once reviewed, an RGA form will be emailed with instructions on how to successfully return your order.

Remember, Docking Drawer waives the restocking fee for exchanges.

​
Docking Drawer Return Policy -

A 0% restocking fee applies to exchanges.
A 15% restocking fee applies to returns within 30 days.
A 25% restocking fee applies to returns within 30 - 60 days.
No returns will be accepted after 60 days.

​Defective products will be replaced at no cost to the customer.

For returns or exchanges, the customer is responsible for paying return shipping. Shipping costs are non-refundable.

settings.type_details:
• Ideal for charging today’s USB technology such as cell phones, tablets, fitness trackers and more.
  • Max Current: 1.5A @ 5VDC per port
  • 2" - The least amount of space needed behind the drawer box
  • Eliminate the need to shorten drawer boxes
  • Ideal for wider drawers
  • Able to charge up to 4 devices at a time
  • Can be specified during any phase of the project, whether it be at the beginning, middle or end.
  • 2 Year Warranty
  • Charging outlet part numbers - 0290-20610W-UK, 0290-20610W-EUR, 0290-20610W-AUS
  • One outlet assembly consists of (2) 45mm modules:
    • Module #1 contains (2) USB-A outlets
    • Module #2 contains (2) USB-A outlets
  • (1) Country specific patch cord included.

• Ideal for powering hair dryers, curling irons and anything requiring 20 amps of service while also providing USB ports to charge today’s USB technology.
  • Interlocking safety feature - Thermostatic Shut Off. Cuts power to the outlet if the temperature rises over 50 degrees celsius
  • Max Current: AC - 10A per outlet @ 240 VAC combined USB - 1.5A @ 5VDC per port
  • May require the drawer to be stepped down a drawer box size or shorted to make room for the outlet
  • Able to charge up to 4 devices at a time
  • Typically specified in the beginning or middle phase of a project
  • 2 Year Warranty
  • Powering outlet part numbers - 0290-20533W-UK, 0290-20533W-EUR, 0290-20533W-AUS
  • One outlet assembly consists of (3) 45mm modules:
